name: The Incident at the Seabrook Residence
name_original: The Incident at the Seabrook Residence
description:
Thank you for joining the ████████████ Digitisation Project!

Case #5772 concerns the Seabrooks, who experienced something in December 2002. There's no need to concern yourself with the details; your job is to clean up the digital files. Sometimes the computer can't read the text we feed it, so we just need someone to manually correct its errors.

Do not concern yourself with the details.
